'''''Chronicle of the Years of Fire''''' ( Arabic    ; French   ; aya mazina yombi asobanura "Chronicle of the Year of Embers ") ni filime yamateka yikinamico yo muri Alijeriya yakinwe muri 1975 iyobowe na Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina<ref>Chronicle of the Years of Fire | Institut français du Royaume-Uni <nowiki>https://www.institut-francais.org.uk</nowiki> › festivals-series › c...</ref> <ref>Chronicle of the years of fire (DVD video, 1997) [WorldCat.org]</ref>. Irerekana Intambara yo kwigenga ya Alijeriya nkuko bigaragara mumaso y'umuhanzi<ref>Chronicle of the Years of Fire - Toronto International Film ... <nowiki>https://www.tiff.net</nowiki> › events › chronicle-of-the-years-of...</ref><ref>A Mohammed Lakhdar-Hamina feature film - africa.film logo <nowiki>https://africa.film</nowiki> › the-chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire-a-...</ref>.

Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya ''Palme d'Or'' mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 1975<ref>Rare screenings at Institut Français's Ciné Lumière <nowiki>https://screenworlds.org</nowiki> › announcements › chronicles-...</ref> <ref>Chronicle of the Years of Fire - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › chronicle-of-the-years-of-fire</ref>.  Yatoranijwe kandi nk'iyinjira muri Alijeriya muri Filime Nziza y'indimi z'amahanga mu bihembo bya 48 bya Academy, ariko ntiyakirwa nk'umukandida.<ref>Cannes Film Festival: every film to win the Palme d'Or - The ... <nowiki>https://www.telegraph.co.uk</nowiki> › films › 1975-chronicle-y...</ref> <ref>Margaret Herrick Library, Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences</ref>

